{"title":"春思","authors":["刘章"],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":1,"day":31}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"春思"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘章"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看北国雪消千嶂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想江南梅花怒放。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遥想那梅香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分明雪也很香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"香入小溪，香入大江，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"约三月桃花汛涨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似觉一缕缕春风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把生命之火吹旺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来胸中艳阳一轮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涌笔下春潮千丈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"静看窗外的阳光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一滴都很有重量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听那缥缈的云间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有春天的脚步声响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有那写春联的笔光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像耕在云霞之上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一笔笔，一字字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种植着幸福、吉祥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿长治久安的日子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像春笋般茁壮；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿每一只蜂蝶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都自由自在地飞翔……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}